title: Gauravam
subTitle: Arjun reaches his friend Shanmughan's village, only to find out that he has eloped with Pasupathy's daughter. So, Arjun, along with his friends and Yazhini, a lawyer, sets out to find the couple.

title: Chandrakala
subTitle: A family moves into their ancestral mansion to try to sell it off. However, trouble starts brewing when they experience supernatural phenomena and a ghost mysteriously killing people.

title: Masthi Maja
subTitle: A comprehensive compilation of some of the most funniest comedy scenes from popular Telugu movies is played back to back.

title: Kevvu Keka
subTitle: Lakshmi's father does not approve of her relationship with her boyfriend, Buchi, as he is not rich. She then challenges him that Buchi will become a millionaire in six months.

title: Kanulu Kanulanu Dochayante
subTitle: Two fraudsters involved in online shopping scams fall in love and eventually decide to give up their shady business, oblivious to the real intentions of the women they love.

title: Tillu Square
subTitle: After a year of getting involved in a murder case due to a love affair, an unlucky disc jockey goes through a dirtier commotion that is related to his past.

title: I
subTitle: A bodybuilder and successful model plans revenge after his enemies inject him with a substance that deforms his body.

title: Atharintiki Daaredi
subTitle: Goutham resolves to reunite his grandfather with Sunanda, his estranged aunt. However, he chooses to pose as a driver to befirend her.

title: Mr. Bachchan
subTitle: Suspended for his honesty, an income tax officer returns to his hometown to live with his family. However, he is soon reinstated and tasked with raiding the home of a corrupt politician.

title: Yenthavaadu Gaani
subTitle: An honest police officer works tirelessly to dismantle an organ trafficking racket. However, he is oblivious that the very man he hunts is his beloved's killer.

title: Vishwaroopam 2
subTitle: Wisam Ahmad Kashmiri, a RAW agent, tries to prevent a terrorist organisation from executing a deadly mission against three countries.

title: Masthi Maja
subTitle: A comprehensive compilation of some of the most funniest comedy scenes from popular Telugu movies is played back to back.

title: Eega
subTitle: Nani loves Bindu but is killed by a jealous businessman, Sudeep, who lusts over Bindu. Nani is reincarnated as a fly and decides to avenge his death and make Sudeep's life a living hell.

title: Samajavaragamana
subTitle: A clerk tutors his father and a female tenant to secure a college degree. Eventually, he falls in love with the girl, leading to a series of comical escapades.

title: Chatrapathi
subTitle: Separated from his family during a conflict, a refugee embarks on a mission to reunite with his adoptive family. However, he faces several challenges after his foster brother conspires against him.

title: Teddy
subTitle: Srividya, a young woman, is put in a coma by corrupt doctors. However, her spirit enters a teddy bear and seeks out a lonely man named Shiva to uncover medical crimes.

title: Nuvve Nuvve
subTitle: Vishwanath is a millionaire who will do anything for his daughter, Anjali. When she falls in love with Rishi, a middle-class boy, he tries everything in his power to end the affair.

title: DJ Tillu
subTitle: Bala Gangadhar Tilak, also known as DJ Tillu, is a young man who wishes to become a disc jockey someday. However, his life changes after he falls in love with Radhika.

title: Om Bheem Bush
subTitle: Three scientists arrive at a village in search of a treasure. However, things take a turn when they explore a haunted palace and discover black magic.

title: Zombie Reddy
subTitle: Chaos ensue as Mario, a game developer, and his gang of friends get entangled in a family feud and an enigmatic zombie attack in Rayalaseema, while attending a friend's wedding.

title: Saptagiri Express
subTitle: A happy-go-lucky actor is forced to do his father's job after his unexpected demise. However, when he realises his father was murdered, he sets out to exact vengeance.

title: MCA: Middle Class Abbayi
subTitle: Nani, a middle-class boy with an eidetic memory, helps save his sister-in-law from a goon. Meanwhile, he also tries to convince his girlfriend's father to marry her off to him.

title: Pokiri
subTitle: Krishna, a police officer, disguises himself as a thug and joins the mafia in order to wipe out the underworld. Meanwhile, he falls in love with Shruti, an aerobics teacher.

title: RRR
subTitle: A fearless revolutionary and an officer in the British force, who once shared a deep bond, decide to join forces and chart out an inspirational path of freedom against the despotic rulers.

title: Raja The Great
subTitle: Raja, a visually impaired young man, steps in to save Lucky from a gangster's deadly pursuit. Subsequently, touched by his unwavering courage and kindness, Lucky falls in love.

title: Salaar
subTitle: Just when the prince of Khansaar is about to rise to the throne, a plan of overthrowing him is exercised and only one man can help him retrieve power.

title: S/O Satyamurthy
subTitle: Anand faces several challenges as he attempts to save his father's wealth while trying to handle the responsibility of earning a livelihood for his family.
